metadata.name: The dreamer
metadata.description:
Glimpses through the interstice of the curtains, slighty drawn. They wrestle with the painful beauty of growing old, unmet needs, dreams unfulfilled, drowning brains, normal pressure hydrocephalus.  

Artwork by Australian artist lilyillo in collaboration with AI, 2023.  

300dpi | 7838px x 10000px | PNG
